high_descs: Turn to your right to face the coffee maker
Pick the mug up from the coffee maker
Turn to your left, move across the room, and turn right to face the white table
Put the mug on the table
Pick up the knife from the table by the apple
Place the knife with handle up in the mug

high_descs: Walk forward slightly and turn right towards the coffee machine.
Pick up the black mug from the coffee machine.
Turn left and walk forward to the door, then turn right towards the dining table.
Put the mug on the dining table, to the right of the spatula.
Pick up the large knife behind the apple on the table.
Put the knife in the black mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it on a dining table.
